<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It is not possible to use the set options like headerCheck or magicfile with the Zend_Validate_File_IsImage validator.
Zend_Validate_File_IsImage does not pass the contructor parameters to Zend_Validate_File_MimeType::__construct method but calls setMimeType. So code for setting these options gets skipped.
I guess this also applys to Zend_Validate_File_IsCompressed (not confirmed).</p>

<p>Calling the parent constructor instead of the setmimetype method fixes the issue, see provided patch. (Not tested via unit tests)</p>

